snippet: Franklin lowered her American record in winning the 200-yard freestyle for the second straight year at the N.C.A.A. women’s swimming and diving championships in Greensboro, N.C.
abstract: Missy Franklin wins 200-yard freestyle at NCAA women's swimming and diving championships in record 1 minute 39.10 seconds.
lead_paragraph: Franklin lowered her American record in winning the 200-yard freestyle for the second straight year at the N.C.A.A. women’s swimming and diving championships in Greensboro, N.C.
